data.Task: Cosco 1 Receipt Generation_archive Data Cloud Flow Fix
data.Notes:
Production process is not running.
Issue root cause identification - someone deleted data from transaction sheet, causing bot to repeatedly add data in the sheet & queues leading to issue.

Sajid reported that the bot had not been running for an extended period. Upon investigation, it was found that certain reference IDs were present in the NOC data Excel but missing from the Transaction data Excel. This mismatch led to an unhandled exception, causing the system to continuously requeue the problematic records. As a result, the bot halted during the process run.
The invalid reference IDs were manually removed from the queue, and the process was closely monitored during execution. The bot has since resumed normal operation and is processing live records successfully. Monitoring will continue to ensure the issue does not recur.
